 up with amazing view of the Bay. Seriously, could they have built this hotel ANY BETTER???? No. It's almost perfect. We had a great weekend stay and once again the service was impeccable. So after such great success last Thanksgiving the parents are flying in from North Carolina and we're going to have a family Thanksgiving in San Francisco for 2009. I'm hoping that all of us have as great an experience as we did the first two times as I've really talked up this hotel to the fam. I will be back with another review if it lives up to the billing I have given it. But in sum, I will say that the rooms with the views and the nicely appointed bathrooms are fantastic. I really like the quaint little lap pool and the googles they give you and the workout room. It's not too big, not too small. The bar and restaurant are both very good and like I said the service is excellent.Here's to hoping 3rd time's the charm. Again!	
