ly accessible from the hotel and we were able to cover the city. Bloomy’s and Neiman Marcus are close if you like shopping. The Chieftain Irish Pub is right across the street and we took advantage of that more than once.All in all, we were very happy with our overall experience and are glad we swung for the room upgrade. Go for it!	
