an regentrification of warehouses, nightspots, residential hotels, art spaces, loft apartments, furniture showrooms, and the infamous Folsom BDSM zone can be sketchy in some blocks, especially around 6th &amp; Mission. The areas by South Park and the Giants ballpark, around the MOMA and Yerba Buena Gardens, and over by 11th &amp; Folsom are the better locales. TIP: Weekend Brunch at TripTych on Folsom.....beignets and benedicts are best.Bottom-line: There may be something comparable in high-end properties but not sure the current promo rate can be beat.	
