ost 6 months ago.Good &quot;management&quot; of our special request - or was it lack of ....whatever ?Anyway - due to the behaviour of the personnel for check-in we decided not to have any meals in the hotel and enjoy the wide variety of choices in the nearby heart of the city. A good decision in San Francisco, and very cost-effective also.Anyway, the hotel was quite a good coice, not an exceptional one.The city is of course - exceptional !	
